Author:
Vol / Page:  765
Edition:
Quote:  In taking a bush hive, honey wax, pollen, propolis, brood and dirt generally get mixed a good deal..which accounts for people being upset after eating bush honey. ..Maoris have been upset after eating honey taken from a bush hive.
